    "For the case of JetsonLab, the frameworks and models were compiled on device with CUDA 12.2.",
    "In order to measure the performance of the respective model on device, we automate the interaction with the chat application.",
    "To accomplish this, we use a set of precanned prompts, sampled from the OAAST chat dataset [51], and interact in a multi-turn manner with the LLM.",
    "More information on the distribution of these prompts in Sec.",
    "5.2.1.For mobile execution, we have used custom native applications 6 that automatically read prompts from a given file and replay the discussion with the model at hand."
